snippet: With inventory falling, the buyer’s market in Grand Cayman of the last few years is giving way to a seller’s market.
abstract: International House Hunting column; five-bedroom house in Vista del Mar, 15-minute walk from beach on Grand Cayman Island, is listed at $4.695 million; information about market and tips for buying on Grand Cayman Island highlighted.
